Name
       timing_cppr_remove_clock_to_data_crp

Syntax
       timing_cppr_remove_clock_to_data_crp

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When set to true, removes clock reconvergence pessimism (CRP) for clock
       source paths.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

